    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 377.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Иқтисодий ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> судига</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 377.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 377.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Ариза берган ташкилотнинг жойлашган манзили</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 377.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берган ташкилотнинг номи, ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва имзо қуйишга ваколатли бўлган мансабдор шахснинг лавозими, Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(Ёзувдаги хатони тўғрилаш юзасидан)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бераман ушбу аризани шу ҳақдаким, иқтисодий ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> суди томонидан <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Даъвогар ташкилотнинг моддий ва маънавий зарарни ундириш ҳақидаги даъво талаби қаноатлантирилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Иш бўйича жавобгар ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий-ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> нисбатан моддий ва маънавий зарарни ундириш ҳақидаги даъво талабимиз қаноатлантириб, жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Иш бўйича жавобгар ташкилотнинг номи ва ташкилий-ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ташкилотимиз фойдасига </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Жавобгар шахсдан ундирилган сумма миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм пул ундириш ҳақида ҳал қилув қарори чиқарилган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мазкур ҳал қилув қарори ижросини таъминлаш мақсадида чиқарилган ижро варақасида ташкилотимиз фойдасига </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Жавобгар шахсдан ундирилган сумма миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм ундириш ўрнига </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Нотўғри ёзилиб кетилган сумма миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм деб нотўғри ёзилиб кетилганлиги сабабли Ўзбекистон Республикаси Иқтисодий процессуал кодексининг </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">347-моддасига асосан ижро варақа ёзувидаги хатони тўғрилаб беришингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Мансабдор шахснинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Мансабдор шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
